{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, more work is needed to validate these approaches in clinical settings and across diverse populations.",
    "This study follows ethical guidelines on data usage, model reliability, and the responsible deployment of large language models (LLMs) for mental health evaluation.",
    "The datasets used in this research, DAIR-AI Emotion and SWMH, are publicly available, ensuring transparency and reproducibility.",
    "The SWMH dataset consists of publicly shared Reddit posts, while the DAIR-AI Emotion dataset contains labeled social media text.",
    "No personally identifiable information (PII) was processed, and no direct engagement with individuals was conducted."
  ]
}